  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: contain; /* Show full image, may have letterboxing */
}
```

**Alternative Fix (Option 2 - Keep current aspect ratio but show full image):**
```css
.cover-card {
  aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
