Start with **Solution 1 (Changing the Container Aspect Ratio)**. It's the cleanest and most reliable fix.  If you need to support very old browsers, consider a fallback.  Avoid Solution 3 unless you have a very specific reason to use it.  Solution 2 is a good alternative if you don't mind the empty space.

